🌿 1️⃣ Delete Local Branch (on your computer)


1️⃣:1️⃣ First switch to another branch:
-------------------------------------------------------
git checkout master
---------------------------------------------------

1️⃣:2️⃣Now delete branch:
----------------------------------------------------
git branch -d rahul2
---------------------------------------------------


🌍 2️⃣ Delete Remote Branch (on GitHub)

To delete branch from GitHub:
--------------------------------------------------
git push origin --delete rahul2
-------------------------------------------------------

______________________________________________________
Delete locally:
git branch -d rahul2
___________________________________________________
Delete on GitHub:
git push origin --delete rahul2
_________________________________________________

🌍 3️⃣  Check Branch List

3️⃣:1️⃣See all branches:

git branch

3️⃣:1️⃣ See remote branches:

git branch -r


🎯 Final Simple Summary
Action	                                             Command
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Delete local branch	                                git branch -d branchname
Force delete local	                                git branch -D branchname
Delete remote branch	                           git push origin --delete branchname
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------